16:
A crude iron bow that, despite
its mass-produced quality,
packs quite a punch.
20:
A bow of fine steel, with
improved durability and power
for more demanding hunts.
24:
A lavish bow of rare steel able
to penetrate even the hardest of
shells with ease.
27:
The Nergigante scales on this
bow continually regrow,
promising unending pain to foes.
29:
Forged from Nergigante parts,
it is drawn to the sinner, its
roar an arrow of holy judgment.
31:
Fortified with thin yet durable
Kulu-Ya-Ku hide, this bow won't
weigh you down.
35:
This perfected Kulu-Ya-Ku bow
grants the agility to dance
circles around any mark.
39:
The extreme weight of this fire-
elemental bow, made of Uragaan
parts, yields extreme damage.
42:
The graceful bend of this bow of
Rathian make brings to mind a
lithe and regal queen.
46:
A bow made host to a Rathalos's
fury, said to be able to rend
earth and sky apart.
50:
New forging techniques have been
used to infuse this iron bow with
the elemental power of water.
54:
Bold yet delicate tweaks have
upped the power and water
element of this iron bow.
58:
The icy, keen-tipped arrows from
this Legiana bow hum as they cut
graceful arcs through the air.
61:
A Legiana bow. Draw, and may any
foe before you be pierced with
your ice-kissed arrows.
64:
A bow made from easily
obtainable bone. Rough-hewn, but
a sturdy friend to new hunters.
68:
Made from the densest of bones,
this bow offers greater piercing
with ease of use.
72:
A bow of modified bone. The
blinding speed of each shot can
easily penetrate solid rock.
75:
Drawing power from beyond death,
this Vaal Hazak bow serves
only those who embrace oblivion.
78:
Harnessing the power of the desert
tyrant, this bow looses arrows
with absolute authority.
81:
The heavy resistance provided by
its twin Diablos horns makes
this bow a challenge to draw.
83:
Any who can so much as draw this
intimidating Black Diablos horn
bow deserves respect.
86:
The Pukei-Pukei's colorful down
hides potent venom, a deadly
secret that catches prey unaware.
90:
The venom-soaked down of the
Pukei-Pukei covering this bow
bristles at the sight of prey.
94:
A bow wrapped in hide tempered
hard as iron in the searing
breath of an Anjanath.
97:
The scorching arrows from this
Anjanath bow cauterize flesh
as they penetrate their prey.
101:
The hank of white Tobi-Kadachi
fur wrapped around this bow is
forever charged with static.
105:
Made of electrified Tobi-Kadachi
parts, this bow amplifies the
static produced when firing.
108:
A dragon element bow hewn
from bone, crafted by dark
and forbidden means.
112:
A dragon element bow forged
in iron, crafted by dark and
forbidden means.
115:
Bearing a flying steed motif,
this Kushala Daora bow is valued
as a work of fine art.
118:
A Xeno'jiiva bow, lord among
treasures. Its pitiless judgment
pierces all before it.
120:
The granddaddy of steel bows.
Designed for ergonomics, it is
remarkably easy to use.
123:
A Bow that requires the strength
of the user. Only those who have
defeated a Deviljho can wield it.
129:
A Kulve Taroth bow with unknown
traits. Its true potential has yet
to be realized.
133:
A Kulve Taroth bow that utilizes
other monster parts for research
purposes.
143:
A Kulve Taroth bow that possesses
new properties due to clever
material utilization.
153:
A Kulve Taroth bow that fully
harnesses the hidden power of
the materials used to create it.
157:
A hidden power seeps from
this Lunastra bow, as if a
soul is trapped inside.
159:
This Lunastra bow was
forged in hellfire. Sometimes
guards its user from fatal blows.
161:
This Lunastra bow resonates
with the added Nergigante parts
to give a chance for regeneration.
163:
This Lunastra bow resonates
with the added Xeno'jiiva parts
to sometimes conserve coatings.
166:
A unique bow made from the
gold of Kulve Taroth. Houses the
true might of the goddess within.
173:
Crafted specifically for the Defense
Corps, its high-performance
output is thanks to modern tech.
191:
Using only the rarest of metals,
this bow can pierce through
even the toughest defense.
195:
A bow made from Zinogre parts.
Its arrows are like fangs that
sunder enemies.
199:
A bow with the dark power of
a Stygian Zinogre. Its arrows
strike foes like bolts of lightning.
202:
Know despair, unrepentant one.
This Ruiner Nergigante bow rains
down bolts upon the iniquitous.
204:
This exquisite Kulu-Ya-Ku bow
grants the agility to dance
circles around any target.
207:
A formidable Brachydios bow.
Its arrows are doused with slime
that explodes inside enemies.
210:
Sends arrows of light hurtling
toward prey with a Raging
Brachydios's explosive speed.
215:
A Pink Rathian bow whose
arrows leave vividly colorful trails,
like a field of blooming flowers.
217:
This bow proves you defeated
a Gold Rathian. Its arrows pierce
the world with everlasting radiance.
219:
Crafted from icy sharp Barioth
parts, this bow freezes prey as
its arrows pierce them.
223:
This bow inherits the burning spirit
of an Azure Rathalos, whose blue
fire is contained within each arrow.
225:
The arch of this Silver Rathalos
bow, radiant like a blazing
sun, proves the wielder's victory.
227:
This bow contains the thunderous
force of a Tigrex, waiting to be
unleashed.
231:
Contrary to its blazing colors,
this Coral Pukei-Pukei bow
drains its prey of heat.
234:
An ebon Bow, black as night.
Nargacuga fur absorbs light,
making it perfect for snipers.
239:
Draw, and let this Shrieking
Legiana bow cause ice to bloom on
your foes like myriad blossoms.
242:
A bow made of only the rarest
bones. Powerful enough to pierce
steel.
246:
The icy shafts of this Velkhana
bow freeze the final cries of
its prey in their throat.
251:
The fallen revel at every shot
from this unerring Blackveil
Vaal Hazak bow.
253:
The faint light shining in this
jet-black Namielle bow is an
invitation into the abyss.
258:
Top-grade Pukei-Pukei down 
steeped in a virulent venom 
grant this bow its lethal bite.
261:
A Nightshade Paolumu bow.
The beautiful black fur glistens
with the blood of its foes.
264:
The undying flame within this
Anjanath bow will see all in
its reach burned to ash.
267:
An untamed Fulgur Anjanath
bow that barely contains the
furious lightning within it.
272:
Only expert craftsmen can handle
the elegant, lethal materials
in this Viper Tobi-Kadachi bow.
276:
A dragon element bow hewn
from bone, crafted by dark
and forbidden means.
279:
Each arrow fired from this Shara
Ishvalda bow leads to paradise,
as lotus stalk leads to blossom.
284:
Take up this Savage Deviljho bow
if you would cede health and sanity
to the revels of endless gorging.
286:
Using the golden fur of a Rajang,
this one-of-a-kind bow looks
like it's been set ablaze.
288:
A Furious Rajang bow that can
only be wielded by those who
have the strength to draw it.
290:
An Alatreon bow desired by those
who lust for power. With this weapon
in hand, they become as dragons.
296:
The bold fur upon this Banbaro
bow sends a challenge to any
brave enough to take it.
299:
Brute Tigrex materials tempered 
black make this bow
spectacularly destructive.
301:
Bestowed upon guild knights with
stellar achievements. The sublime
glow is a source of pride.
303:
This Glavenus bow stokes the
flame of a hunter's passion to
sear all who dare oppose.
306:
The acid flowing from the tip
of this Acidic Glavenus bow
weakens its prey from within.
312:
A silver Frostfang Barioth bow
enveloped by a sharp cold.
Proof of the hoarfrost's keeper.
314:
The whir of the wicked arrows
fired from this Fatalis bow
sing a prelude to destruction.
317:
A bow that gleams with the glow
of the azure star. Its essence lies
within hunters ready to stand tall.
327:
A bow made from Safi'jiiva parts.
Awaken its hidden potential by
using unique materials.
